@startuml
title Benchmark Sequence Diagram

actor User as U
participant "gen_zero_shot.py" as G
participant "export_views.py" as V
participant "build_model_io_json.py" as C
participant "model runner" as R
participant "eval_predictions.py" as E
participant "annotate_model_outputs.py" as A

U -> G : Generate raw note-level benchmark
G --> V : zero_shot.json
V --> C : tokenizer views
C --> R : model-ready cases
R --> E : predictions.json
R --> A : predictions.json
E --> U : overall / by_task / by_tokenizer
A --> U : cases_with_outputs / summary

note over E, A
Standard mode scores labels or note sequences.
Explanatory mode preserves optional prediction_explanation.
end note

@enduml
